I would rather we had increased support spells instead of a pet.  A pet of that magnitude might make us a pet class which is not what the Sorc is all about.  Besides, I think pets suck in RvR because they are built for the PvE world and the chaos of human players running from your pet makes them ineffective.  I would rather have a bolt range single target mez, or debuffs that are effective.  Something to complement our cc abilites like Amnesia and Confusion working in RvR.  Besides, having a lvl 55 pet would probably be seen as too unbalancing by our peers.<P>I'm going to spec to 50 in mind anyway on faith that Mythic will get it together and make Mind viable (GO i3ullseye !!!)<P>--------------------<P>Toadstool, THE Newbie Sorc, Kay
