I would like to see them buff up pets so that they are more effective depending on their proximity to you the caster.  That way you trade off the danger of getting agro of the ability to have a more effective pet.  It would make sense for the class sense you are exerting mental effort to maintain the pet and the close the pet is to you the easier it is to exert that force on your servant.<P>--------------------<P>Toadstool, THE Newbie Sorc, Kay
